Installation:
	anarchy installer
	don't install opensource drivers
	uefi installation
	zsh from installer
	grub (?)

Post installation:
Packages:
	bzip2, code, compton, dmenu, feh, firefox, gcc, git, gzip, htop, lightdm, lightdm-gtk-greeter-settings,
	mpv, neofetch, nerdfonts (dots use source code pro/hermit/roboto), polybar, ranger, rofi, scrot, sxhkd, tar, unzip, rofi-menus-git,
	thunar

Install powerlevel10k

GTK customization: install lxappearance, ach-gtk-theme, breeze cursor, deepin/breeze icons (start lxappearance as sudo to make changes)
